data.description: Charming home, with a decent sized yard and mature trees! Front yard has a new tree planted. New exterior paint. Flooring on stairway and upstairs have been re done. Minor renovations in bathroom have been done as well. Refrigerator, stove, and microwave do convey. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, dining, and Sea world!
